{"tid":1950281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"哈里夫婦棄加前往LA 美國總統特拉普指他與英國及皇室是Good friend，但美國不會為兩夫婦支付保安費","createTime":"2020-03-30T08:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T10:46:19.000Z","uid":133680,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a02a2e9c7abe2716f816d3090a48d4411a7f4cea","tid":1950281,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:42:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E5%93%88%E9%87%8C%E7%8E%8B%E5%AD%90&amp;sxsrf=ALeKk03H9vAtMk7NpiANaU-aX41JjmzG6g:1585557613701&amp;source=lnms&amp;tbm=nws&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjAodey5sHoAhXVVBUIHSnIDM0Q_AUoAnoECBgQBA&amp;biw=1600&amp;bih=789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%25E5%2593%2588%25E9%2587%258C%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%25AD%2590%26sxsrf%3DALeKk03H9vAtMk7NpiANaU-aX41JjmzG6g%3A1585557613701%26source%3Dlnms%26tbm%3Dnws%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjAodey5sHoAhXVVBUIHSnIDM0Q_AUoAnoECBgQBA%26biw%3D1600%26bih%3D789&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2Ux5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=3e496b07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/search?q=%E5%93%88%E9%87%8C%E7%8E%8B%E5%AD%90&amp;sxsrf=ALeKk03H9vAtMk7NpiANaU-aX41JjmzG6g:1585557613701&amp;source=lnms&amp;tbm=nws&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjAodey5sHoAhXVVBUIHSnIDM0Q_AUoAnoECBgQBA&amp;biw=1600&amp;bih=789</a><br />\n<br />\n哈里與梅根將定居洛杉磯，特朗普指不會支付其保安費。AP<br />\n哈里和梅根已經離開加拿大，準備定居美國洛杉磯。對此，特朗普在社交平台上表態，美國不會為兩人支付安保費，他們必須自費。<br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒報道，宣布淡出英國王室的哈里王子和梅根夫婦，上星期已經搬到梅根成長的洛衫磯居住。美國總統特朗普在社交網站貼文，指美國不會為哈里夫婦支付保安費用。特朗普指他是英女王和英國的好朋友和仰慕者，但他們必須支付相關費用。<br />\n<br />\n英媒稱，哈里和梅根離開加拿大來美國是為了避免支付兩筆重稅。如果兩人長居美國，將會產生每年800萬英鎊的安保費用。一項民意調查顯示，超過90%民眾認為哈里和梅根應該自己買單。<br />\n<br />\n哈里夫婦透過發言人表示，已經作出私人財政資助的保安安排，無意要求美國政府提供保安資源。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，哈里夫婦早前表示希望淡出王室，其後達成協議，將會在本月31日正式放棄王室頭銜，不再接受任何公款資助。"},{"pid":"ad3ff3b9cd0941ba1f88f6f1155b45c084586019","tid":1950281,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:43:33.000Z","msg":"想做美國王子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73f35169485416fce7d517c0621b54970b5b924","tid":1950281,"uid":229037,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:43:34.000Z","msg":"我諗咗好耐邊鬼個叫特拉普"},{"pid":"9a7dc043bbdd0fba2876875736ebc480f0ca32ac","tid":1950281,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c581afb2331bb3e30649d179cfcc2307c0bfa7","tid":1950281,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b73f35169485416fce7d517c0621b54970b5b924","tid":1950281,"uid":229037,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:43:34.000Z","msg":"我諗咗好耐邊鬼個叫特拉普"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:47:54.000Z","msg":"侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25be45bca2925a9f7e72489b521f0496def10148","tid":1950281,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf475d22ac7aa14d2144b39d215f613f1058b61","tid":1950281,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"48c581afb2331bb3e30649d179cfcc2307c0bfa7","tid":1950281,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b73f35169485416fce7d517c0621b54970b5b924","tid":1950281,"uid":229037,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:43:34.000Z","msg":"我諗咗好耐邊鬼個叫特拉普"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:47:54.000Z","msg":"侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:01:17.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba631f9bc3136e885ada4f8ab3d